race.comment: GRAY ELLIOT (7) was below best at his last start when 7th at this track following a third place finish (25.79) at Ballarat two back. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Key runner on his best form. ASTON CASTLE (1) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing second (23.25) and beaten 0.8 lengths over 400m at Mt Gambier. Expected to be in this for a long way. BOB DEEDS (2) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (22.62) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Leading chance. BUSH LASS (8) is always a threat when she races at this track and distance.
